This comprehensive guide should provide you with a deep understanding of disability claim management. As you work in the software development, focus on:

Understanding the "why" behind each process - helps you design better solutions
Regulatory compliance - non-negotiable in insurance
User experience - both for adjusters and claimants
Data accuracy and security - critical for medical information
Automation opportunities - where technology can improve efficiency
